I"S<p>發現上圖寫個 web 後台有些麻煩  , scp 又有些麻煩最簡單就是</p>

<p>網芳了 samba 的 /etc/samba/smb.conf 設定如下 :</p>

<hr />
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>[global]
        workgroup = SAMBA
        security = user

        passdb backend = tdbsam

[web_php]
    path = /var/www/html/prog
    force user = apache
    browseable = No
    read only = No
    inherit acls = Yes

[web_picture]
    path = /var/www/html/image
    force user = apache
    browseable = No
    read only = No
    inherit acls = Yes
</code></pre></div></div>
<hr />
<p>加入 user 帳號 apache (看你的 web 帳號 …我的是 apache )
———-</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>smbpasswd -a  apache 
</code></pre></div></div>
